{"tid":2291057,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英擬就DQ立會議員制裁中港官員    劉曉明批評違反國際義務","createTime":"2020-11-18T12:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T15:39:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2bff6c309d6a3467c4bd2701bb1a908bd29f12cb","tid":2291057,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9dbYM_HVjEcqNK5NvnglvA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ni44NDIxMDUyNjMxNTc5/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/ccc66950-295b-11eb-bc8f-1f062c637b02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9dbYM_HVjEcqNK5NvnglvA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ni44NDIxMDUyNjMxNTc5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-11%2Fccc66950-295b-11eb-bc8f-1f062c637b02&h=9a40abef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國外相藍韜文曾批評北京再度違反《中英聯合聲明》。（Getty Images圖片）<br />\n香港4名泛民主派人士被取消立法會議員資格（DQ），英國日前批評中方違反《中英聯合聲明》，並表示考慮制裁中港官員，作為回應的一部分。中國駐英國大使劉曉明周二（17日）出席網上會議時回應有關提問，批評英方違反國際義務，強調全國人大常委會關於香港立法會議員資格的決定合理、合法、合憲。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明出席英國中國商會、48間集團俱樂部、英中貿協、英中協會聯合舉辦的中共十九屆五中全會精神在線宣介會，發表題為《把握新機遇，注入新信心，開啟新征程》的主題演講，暗批美國大搞單邊主義、保護主義、霸權主義，鼓吹「新冷戰」和「脫鈎論」，威脅國際社會穩定和安全。<br />\n<br />\n被問及英國外交部針對香港立法會議員問題，多次指摘中國違反國際義務和《中英聯合聲明》，中方將作甚麼反應時，劉曉明稱自己因涉港問題被英國外交部常務次官召見，已在會上向對方闡明中方立場。他批評，英國干涉香港事務和中國內政，就是違反國際義務的行為。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明指，中英關係面臨的一大問題是，互相尊重主權和領土完整、互不干涉內政的國際關係基本準則遭到破壞，強調中方仍然重視中英關係，若政治互信受損，整體雙邊關係便會受影響。他呼籲英方珍惜來之不易的中英關係，與中方相向而行，共同推動兩國關係早日重歸正軌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/英擬就dq立會議員制裁中港官員-劉曉明批評違反國際義務-051457390.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E8%8B%B1%E6%93%AC%E5%B0%B1dq%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1-%E5%8A%89%E6%9B%89%E6%98%8E%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%BE%A9%E5%8B%99-051457390.html&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5hx0icFY2nnrImD0qQ%2FuO9w%3D&h=22416b76\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/英擬就dq立會議員制裁中港官員-劉曉明批評違反國際義務-051457390.html</a>"},{"pid":"533415fe0c5eed40866cdf7e303cacb7118ce429","tid":2291057,"uid":321002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"LIKE祼女，就有理有據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd3c04f0539a0bc678a27182dfb70e7fb4f9702","tid":2291057,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"What is國際義務<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d59873e83fa0f30bf16522bb8f7aa92c530c47","tid":2291057,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c041d2da597ca7e9b679cf1ea92e31252757638","tid":2291057,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9d59873e83fa0f30bf16522bb8f7aa92c530c47","tid":2291057,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:42:30.000Z","msg":"係 英中聯合聲明"},{"pid":"f9a5e91e92b3ef8b0cc4ed005188b58d8bd29583","tid":2291057,"uid":137999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:46:08.000Z","msg":"支共對別國內政說三道四"},{"pid":"f598168f60ef49ddb9ed2c7a3d1639af36ab0691","tid":2291057,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e9810cd5d5c5a4f9e00bc70fd19df727f018a4","tid":2291057,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1